tion":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Alright, onto the lesson!","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID304","SecondaryAttribute":"Being attuned to customer concerns during a major shift in company structure can help ensure thos...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<i>Being attuned to customer concerns during a major shift in company structure can help ensure those customers are satisfied.<\/i>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Being attuned to customer concerns during a major shift in company structure can help ensure thos...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<i>Companies that package their products in ways that superficially resemble those of more fragile products can reduce damages due to shipping.<\/i>","DataExportTag":"Q304","QuestionID":"QID304"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID96","SecondaryAttribute":"Business school professors studied the case you read and summarized it as follows: Companies that...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<i>Business school professors studied the case you read and summarized it as follows:<\/i><br>\n<br>\n<strong>Companies that package their products in boxes that superficially resemble those of more fragile products may reduce damages due to shipping.<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q96","QuestionID":"QID96","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Business school professors studied the case you read and summarized it as follows: Companies that...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID95","SecondaryAttribute":"Business school professors studied the case you were shown and summarized it as follows: Companie...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Business school professors studied the case you were shown and summarized it as follows:<br><br><i>Companies that package their products in boxes that superficially resemble those of more fragile products may reduce damages due to shipping.<\/i><br>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Business school professors studied the case you were shown and summarized it as follows: Companie...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"MinChar","MinChars":"5"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"The information you were shown derives from this case study:<br><br>Dutch bicycle manufacturer VanMoof found that it had a problem. As it shipped its products to customers, it found that many bicycles were arriving to customers damaged.\n\nThe damage reports were a major problem for the company because the company\u2019s bikes are high-end, and some are loaded down with delicate electronics like anti-theft trackers and electric motors. Plus, the company had set a goal to sell 90 percent of its bikes online by the end of the decade.<br><br>&nbsp;The company came up with a solution: print a graphic of a flatscreen television on the side of the box. By making shippers think that they were transporting flatscreen televisions, the company found instantaneous results: shipping damage dropped by 70-80 percent. Nobody wants to damage a new television.<i><\/i><br><br>Please try to write anything the first thing you read taught you that the case study did not.<br>","DataExportTag":"Q95","QuestionID":"QID95"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID318","SecondaryAttribute":"Business schools have been criticized for giving lessons of inconsistent quality. So, we want you...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Business schools have been criticized for giving lessons of inconsistent quality. <br><br>So, we want your help in giving an accurate assessment of the quality of a randomly selected lesson. It may be good; it may be bad; and it may be somewhere in between.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q318","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Business schools have been criticized for giving lessons of inconsistent quality. So, we want you...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID318"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID208","SecondaryAttribute":"By how much were VanMoof's shipping costs reduced after implementing the employee's solution?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"By how much were VanMoof's shipping costs reduced after implementing the employee's solution?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"man","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"By how much were VanMoof's shipping costs reduced after implementing the employee's solution?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Virtually 0%: The solution did not work"},"2":{"Display":"50-60%"},"3":{"Display":"60-70%"},"4":{"Display":"70-80%"},"5":{"Display":"80-90%"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":7,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID208","Randomization":{"Advanced":null,"Type":"All","TotalRandSubset":""}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1","SecondaryAttribute":"Click to write the question text","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Click to write the question text","DataExportTag":"Q1","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Click to write the question text","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Click to write Choice 1"},"2":{"Display":"Click to write Choice 2"},"3":{"Display":"Click to write Choice 3"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID1"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID5","SecondaryAttribute":"Click to write the question text","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Click to write the question text","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q5","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Click to write the question text","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID5"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID16","SecondaryAttribute":"Click to write the question text","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Click to write the question text","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q16","QuestionType":"Slider"