option.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please select the middle option.<br>","DataExportTag":"att_s","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAHR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","LabelPosition":"BELOW"},"QuestionDescription":"Please select the middle option.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Extremely difficult"},"2":{"Display":"Moderately difficult"},"3":{"Display":"Somewhat difficult"},"4":{"Display":"Neither difficult nor easy"},"5":{"Display":"Somewhat easy"},"6":{"Display":"Moderately easy"},"7":{"Display":"Extremely easy"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6","7"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":8,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID327"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID328","SecondaryAttribute":"Please select the middle option.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please select the middle option.<br>","DataExportTag":"att_t","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAHR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","LabelPosition":"BELOW"},"QuestionDescription":"Please select the middle option.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Extremely difficult"},"2":{"Display":"Moderately difficult"},"3":{"Display":"Somewhat difficult"},"4":{"Display":"Neither difficult nor easy"},"5":{"Display":"Somewhat easy"},"6":{"Display":"Moderately easy"},"7":{"Display":"Extremely easy"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6","7"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":8,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID328"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID42","SecondaryAttribute":"Please share what the above taught you","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please share what the above taught you","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please share what the above taught you","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"CharRange","MinChars":"5","TotalChars":"140","ContentType":null,"ValidDateType":"DateWithFormat","ValidPhoneType":"ValidUSPhone","ValidZipType":"ValidUSZip","ValidNumber":{"Min":"","Max":"","NumDecimals":""}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please share what the above taught you","DataExportTag":"Q42","QuestionID":"QID42"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID4","SecondaryAttribute":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking technologies contributes to the financial, critical, and cultural success of the cinematic production in which those new technologies were utilized.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"gd.gg","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID4"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID8","SecondaryAttribute":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking technologies could perhaps contribute to the financial, critical, and cultural success of the movie in which those new technologies were utilized.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"gp.gg","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID8"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID11","SecondaryAttribute":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking technologies contributes to the financial, critical, and cultural success of the cinematic production in which those new technologies were utilized.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"sd.gg","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Risking experimentation with and (ultimately) implementation of novel, still untested filmmaking...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID11"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID289","SecondaryAttribute":"Sometimes it can be lucrative for a company to improve the simplicity and speed of delivery rathe...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<i>Sometimes it can be lucrative for a company to improve the simplicity and speed of delivery rather than improve the product itself.<\/i>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Sometimes it can be lucrative for a company to improve the simplicity and speed of delivery rathe...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<i>Companies that package their products in ways that superficially resemble those of more fragile products can reduce damages due to shipping.<\/i>","DataExportTag":"att_f","QuestionID":"QID289"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID228","SecondaryAttribute":"The Edwards family pooled $35,000 of their own money to produce their homeopathic cure for consti...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<i>The Edwards family pooled $35,000 of their own money to produce their homeopathic cure for constipation: the Squatty Potty. With no money left to market the Potty, the family decided to simply give it away to various health media influencers on Instagram, Facebook, and Twitter. Despite spending no money on advertising, sales of the product quickly rose to $28,000, and caught the attention of Dr. Oz, Howard Stern, and Shark Tank, bringing Squatty Potty to an annual revenue of $12 million.<\/i>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"The Edwards family pooled $35,000 of their own money to produce their homeopathic cure for consti...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<i>Dutch bicycle manufacturer VanMoof found that it had a problem. As it shipped its products to customers, it found that many bicycles were arriving to customers damaged.\n<br><br>The damage reports were a major problem for the company because the company\u2019s bikes are high-end, and some are loaded down with delicate electronics like anti-theft trackers and electric motors. Plus, the company had set a goal to sell 90 percent of its bikes online by the end of the decade.\n<br><br>One of the employees came up with a solution: print a graphic of a flatscreen television on the side of the box. By making shippers think that they were transporting flatscreen televisions, the company found that shipping damage dropped by 70-80 percent. Nobody wants to damage a new television.<\/i>","DataExportTag":"Q228","QuestionID":"QID228"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID129","SecondaryAttribute":"The following information was taken from a lesson given by a business instructor. The instructor...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>The following information was taken from a lesson given by a business instructor.<br><br>The instructor gave this real-world case study.<\/b>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q129","QuestionID":"QID129","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"The following information was taken from a lesson given by a business instructor. The instructor...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9SsLUX1YLBxRm6i","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID151","SecondaryAttribute":"The following information was taken from a lesson given by a business instructor. The instructor...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>The following information was taken from a lesson given by a business instructor. <br><br>The instructor gave this message.<\/b>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisi